&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beyond powers the business of short-term rentals with a best-in-class Revenue Management System used by thousands of property managers and owners around the world. We’re profitable, growing fast, and building with the latest technologies—including AI—to help our customers unlock more revenue with less effort. Behind our product is a global team of 180+ Beyonders who bring curiosity, craft, and care to everything we do. We believe people are the most important part of any business, starting with ours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&#39;s with that in mind that Beyond is looking to add a Business Development Representative to our growing team. Reporting to the Manager of Business Development, you will have the opportunity to play a key role in prospecting new business for the company. We believe in bringing your whole self to work. We are committed to building a diverse team and embracing an inclusive culture. If you are looking to get in on the ground floor of a high-growth startup and be a part of a founding sales team, we’re excited to chat with you. This is a hybrid role with 2-3 days per week in our Chicago office and 2-3 days remote.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before reading further...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beyond is passionate about diversity and cultivating our team’s potential. If you’re hungry for a good opportunity, but don&#39;t meet every point in this job description, please apply anyway!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Business Development Representative, you&#39;ll be responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sourcing, reaching out to, and qualifying leads to convey Beyond’s value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Converting qualified leads into scheduled product demos for our Account Executive team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating cross-functionally to share and learn from best practices&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quota attainment based on qualified leads &amp;amp; activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So what kind of person are we looking for in this role? The person who will be successful in this role will be:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hardworking:&lt;/strong&gt; You are highly self-motivated to succeed, driven to exceed your goals and targets, and eager to learn and grow professionally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative: &lt;/strong&gt;You are able to work cross functionally and act as a strong teammate who partners driving success for local and global stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Able to prioritize: &lt;/strong&gt;You are able to handle multiple tasks to prioritize and execute in a dynamic fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outbound-driven: &lt;/strong&gt;You thrive sourcing, prospecting and reaching out to clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now that we’ve told you what the job looks like, here are the qualifications we&#39;re looking for in a candidate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A demonstrated ability to understand and apply effective outbound prospecting strategies and techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence in picking up the phone and smoothly conversing with prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated history of resilience, curiosity, optimism, and a solutions-oriented mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of overachieving against defined metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A data-oriented approach with an aptitude for large data sets and numbers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A desire to win, doesn’t believe in settling, and finds motivation in temporary setbacks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus Points for experience with Salesforce and Sales Automation/Engagement platform and/or familiarity with Property Management Systems and/or the vacation rental market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
